         <abstract label="Abstract">Inventory includes papers,
         1862-1868, of the Martin family of North Carolina, chiefly the
         correspondence of Major Thomas Alston Martin who served in the
         13th North Carolina Infantry. Includes letters, 1862, of R. C.
         Martin written while serving in the Confederate Army. Many
         letters in the collection are written by women.</abstract>
         <origination label="Creator">
            <famname>Martin Family.</famname>
         </origination>
      </did>
